1
00:01:12,756 --> 00:01:17,280
Hold your head up straight. 把頭抬起來
Yes, like that. 對，就這樣

2
00:01:20,013 --> 00:01:22,975
One, two, three
一、二、三

3
00:01:24,996 --> 00:01:27,985
Ok, great. 好，很好
Now we'll change the background. 
現在我們要換背景了

4
00:01:28,164 --> 00:01:30,164
Go and change it. 請幫我換背景
OK. 好的

5
00:01:36,995 --> 00:01:38,995
Gently does it.
小心一點喔

6
00:01:50,992 --> 00:01:52,992
Yes, that's good.
好 這樣很好

7
00:01:53,492 --> 00:01:55,036
Is that OK? 這樣可以嗎？
It's fine. 嗯嗯可以

8
00:01:55,152 --> 00:01:57,009
OK, everyone, look this way.
好了各位，請看這邊

9
00:01:58,010 --> 00:02:01,051
Hey, little boy, over here!
哈囉！小男生看這邊喔！

10
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:04,095
One, two, three.
一、二、三

11
00:02:12,755 --> 00:02:14,123
OK, that's good.
嗯，這樣好

12
00:02:14,196 --> 00:02:17,104
Now for the next lot. 好換下一組人
Come on. 來吧

13
00:02:20,094 --> 00:02:22,190
Print out their photo for them.
記得把照片洗給他們

14
00:02:23,089 --> 00:02:24,038
OK.
好的

15
00:02:27,122 --> 00:02:29,222
Here, this is for the photo
這是拍照的答謝

16
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:35,110
Right then
好的

17
00:02:39,047 --> 00:02:41,010
Two... 兩張...
And this... 還有這些...

18
00:02:42,021 --> 00:02:45,987
That makes 17. 這樣就17了
Come on, let's go. 好了，我們走吧

19
00:02:48,168 --> 00:02:49,152
Ah, the stool.
阿，有凳子。

20
00:02:49,230 --> 00:02:53,809
17 yuan, it's expensive! 17元！好貴唷
Petrol, paper, ink. Everything's gone up.
石油，紙，墨水，什麼都漲了。

21
00:02:56,389 --> 00:02:57,006
OK, I'm ready.
好，我準備好了喔。

22
00:02:58,073 --> 00:02:59,506
Everything except incomes!
什麼都漲就是薪水沒漲！

23
00:03:00,229 --> 00:03:01,236
Shall we do it, then?
我們開始吧，好嗎？

24
00:03:03,009 --> 00:03:04,980
No, wait. You two change places.
等一下喔，你們倆交換一下

25
00:03:05,019 --> 00:03:07,791
You there and you here.
你去那邊 你在這邊

26
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,988
We can't see you… That's better.
我們看不到你...這樣好多了

27
00:03:17,032 --> 00:03:19,020
That's it.
對，就這樣

28
00:03:20,055 --> 00:03:21,075
Shall we do it?
可以開始了嗎？

29
00:03:22,023 --> 00:03:23,055
Hurry up!
快一點！

30
00:03:24,003 --> 00:03:25,009
Oh, him too.
喔，還有他。

31
00:03:25,247 --> 00:03:27,990
Take his work jacket off.
把他的外套脫掉

32
00:03:30,084 --> 00:03:31,102
Give that here.
這放這邊。

33
00:03:35,089 --> 00:03:37,151
- How's this? 這樣可以嗎？
- Yes, it's better. 嗯好多了

34
00:03:47,139 --> 00:03:48,183
Ah, the little one.
阿，還有小朋友

35
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:53,992
Careful now, be gentle.
阿小心點唷！小心小心

36
00:03:56,111 --> 00:03:58,023
Hold him tight.
抓緊他

37
00:03:58,212 --> 00:04:01,140
Maybe not that tight. 不要這麼緊好了
No, not like that. 不，不是這樣

38
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,640
Gently and higher up. 輕輕的然後往上
That’s good. 這樣好

39
00:04:05,186 --> 00:04:07,186
Everyone, look over here.
好了，大家看這邊

40
00:04:08,223 --> 00:04:11,214
One, two, three
一、二、三

41
00:04:17,130 --> 00:04:18,220
Grandaad.
外公

42
00:04:19,081 --> 00:04:21,230
-Can you wear this? 可以請您穿這個嘛？
-Yes 好阿

43
00:04:23,019 --> 00:04:26,074
- Can you try it for size? 你可以試一下尺寸嘛？
- It'll be fine. 沒關係啦

44
00:04:31,145 --> 00:04:33,145
A top-of-the-range jacket!
鑽石高檔外套！

45
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:39,118
There.
好多了

46
00:04:42,096 --> 00:04:45,112
Here, son, can you wear this? 那兒子可以請你穿這個嘛？
Try it on. 試試看

47
00:04:57,218 --> 00:04:59,005
Or, if not that...
呃...那不要這件...

48
00:05:00,115 --> 00:05:02,065
Herem have this one.
繼承人我們穿這件好嗎？

49
00:05:06,052 --> 00:05:07,219
Gongbo! Gongbo...

50
00:05:10,098 --> 00:05:12,060
Too bad for him. Come back.
他在幹什麼，叫他回來

51
00:05:21,016 --> 00:05:24,006
It doesn't matter. 沒關係的
Stand there. OK, that's good. 好那我們站這邊

52
00:05:26,025 --> 00:05:29,213
Everyone, look at me. 大家看我這邊
Little one, look over here. 小朋友看過來唷

53
00:05:30,174 --> 00:05:32,037
Look at me!
看我！

54
00:05:33,135 --> 00:05:34,169
This way.
看這邊

55
00:05:35,003 --> 00:05:38,112
One, two, three.
一、二、三

56
00:05:41,090 --> 00:05:43,115
- Where did you get the beads? 
你在哪找到這些珠珠阿？
- Lhassa. 拉薩

57
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:48,115
Youngsters don't wear old clothes
any more, like the kid earlier. 
現在很少有年輕人像剛剛那位願意穿傳統服飾了

58
00:05:49,051 --> 00:05:56,033
His mother made it for him.
Now she's dead, he always wears it.
那件是他媽媽做的，他媽死後他總是穿那件

59
00:06:02,025 --> 00:06:06,977
Help me with this tie, my friend. 朋友，可以幫我一下嗎？
OK. 沒問題

60
00:06:15,025 --> 00:06:16,036
Come on. 來吧

61
00:06:22,115 --> 00:06:25,218
The knot should be inside. There.
這結要在裡面，好了

62
00:06:30,002 --> 00:06:32,002
- How's that? 可以嗎？
- Perfect. 很好

63
00:06:36,089 --> 00:06:39,949
A bit more this way. 再過來一點點
And you, in the middle. 然後你，站中間

64
00:06:41,134 --> 00:06:42,105
The flower. 那個花

65
00:06:52,045 --> 00:06:54,993
Now, both of you, look over here.
好，現在兩位都看這邊

66
00:06:57,236 --> 00:06:59,861
Look over here. 看這裡
Hey! 嘿！

67
00:07:02,017 --> 00:07:05,173
- Mr Mayor, a cigarette? 市長！抽煙嗎？
- No, thanks. 不用了

68
00:07:07,167 --> 00:07:10,010
As you're all here, 既然你們都在，
I have some announcements. 我有事情要宣布

69
00:07:11,021 --> 00:07:16,010
For the New Socialist Campaign, 
the authorities will be visiting us.
為了新社會主義運動，當局要來探訪我們

70
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:22,146
Everyone must clean their home, 每個人
inside and out. 都要把家裡打掃徹底

71
00:07:23,206 --> 00:07:28,107
Also, a sacred yak belonging 另外 Lahmo 有隻
to Lahmo Tso has been stolen. 神聖的蝥牛被偷了

72
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:34,958
There must be strangers around. 
這裡一定有陌生人，我們會調查的
We'll investigate it.

73
00:07:42,108 --> 00:07:45,012
Goodbye! 再見！

74
00:07:46,222 --> 00:07:48,110
Wait! 等一下！

75
00:08:08,011 --> 00:08:10,036
Come and sit here. 你坐過來。

76
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:14,200
- The motorbike's a good idea. 摩托車是個好點子
- Yes, it’s brand-new. 對阿！這全新的

77
00:08:17,029 --> 00:08:19,029
There's a flower there. 這裡有束花
Put it on the motorbike. 把它放在摩托車上吧

78
00:08:21,073 --> 00:08:25,011
- You have lots of props. 你好多道具喔
- It's my job. 這是我的工作

79
00:08:25,175 --> 00:08:27,175
- You like that? 你喜歡嗎？
- Yes. 喜歡

80
00:08:28,173 --> 00:08:30,161
Knot it underneath. 在下面打結吧

81
00:08:34,048 --> 00:08:35,116
Perfect. 太棒了

82
00:08:36,128 --> 00:08:38,153
Look over here, both of you.
來，兩個人都看這邊

83
00:08:39,119 --> 00:08:41,119
And smile. That's it.
笑一個，很好

84
00:08:41,196 --> 00:08:44,001
One, two, three.
一、二、三

85
00:09:01,126 --> 00:09:03,051
Hey, clear off!
嘿！清場清場！

86
00:09:06,228 --> 00:09:09,021
Hold it in your hand.
把它拿好

87
00:09:10,069 --> 00:09:12,143
You too, hold it like that.
你也是，這樣拿著

88
00:09:15,171 --> 00:09:17,046
Look over here.
來，看這邊

89
00:09:18,069 --> 00:09:19,091
Over here!
看這邊！

90
00:09:19,205 --> 00:09:20,107
One, two...
一、二...

91
00:09:22,002 --> 00:09:24,002
- No, don't! 不要！
- Don’t take it off him. 別把它拿走

92
00:09:24,228 --> 00:09:27,003
Don't do that again. 不要再這樣了喔
Look over here. 看這邊

93
00:09:27,179 --> 00:09:29,179
Keep still. 不要動

94
00:09:30,078 --> 00:09:33,049
One, two, three.
一、二、三

95
00:09:40,199 --> 00:09:42,037
Come on, clear off!
好了！清場！

96
00:09:43,147 --> 00:09:44,233
You too, over here!
你也是，看這邊！

97
00:09:46,227 --> 00:09:49,013
Go and look at yourself 快去看
on the photos. 去看你的照片

98
00:09:53,124 --> 00:09:55,199
- Ah, here's Grandma! 阿！這是奶奶！
- Yes. 是阿

99
00:09:56,047 --> 00:09:58,197
This is Ama Lhamo Tso. 這是 Ama
I mentioned her earlier. 我們剛剛有提過她

100
00:09:59,108 --> 00:10:01,233
She's never 她從來沒有拍過照片
been photographed before.

101
00:10:03,016 --> 00:10:06,163
- We'll make it special. 我們會拍一張很棒的
- Do you have other backgrounds? 
你還有其他的背景嗎？

102
00:10:07,012 --> 00:10:08,199
Of course. 當然
Bring the catalogue. 幫我把目錄拿來

103
00:10:11,152 --> 00:10:13,041
- Come and see. 你來看看
- OK. 好的

104
00:10:16,007 --> 00:10:19,000
- This one? 這個呢？
- It's nice, but not for her. 這不錯，但不適合她

105
00:10:21,019 --> 00:10:24,147
- Or this? 還是這個呢？
- Yes, that's good. 嗯！這個好

106
00:10:27,187 --> 00:10:29,187
Lower that one. 把這降下來

107
00:10:31,244 --> 00:10:34,222
- The motorbike was nice of you. 謝謝你的摩托車
- It was no big deal. 這沒什麼

108
00:10:35,145 --> 00:10:38,065
- What village are you from? 你是哪個村子來的？
- I'm from here. 我就是這邊來的

109
00:10:38,229 --> 00:10:41,140
How many people live in the village?
有多少人住在這個村莊？

110
00:10:42,026 --> 00:10:45,125
- 248 households. 有248戶
- That's a lot. 哇那很多耶

111
00:10:46,048 --> 00:10:49,063
But the youngsters 但是年輕人
all go off to town to work. 都跑出村莊工作了

112
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:52,032
- How's that? 這樣怎麼樣？
- Yes, perfect. 嗯，很好

113
00:10:53,043 --> 00:10:56,146
It's her dream 有一天去看看布達拉宮
to visit Potala Palace one day. 是她的夢想

114
00:10:59,074 --> 00:11:02,165
When the road's finished 等路蓋好
it'll be easier to get here. 就會比較方便過去的

115
00:11:02,229 --> 00:11:04,217
Yes, we'll save over ten hours.
對阿！會省下十個小時耶

116
00:11:05,128 --> 00:11:07,228
- When will it be finished? 什麼時候會蓋好呢？
- By spring. 這個春天

117
00:11:08,114 --> 00:11:12,032
Oh, no, she's prostrating herself! 
喔不！她自己膜拜了起來
Up you get, Grandma. 奶奶起來吧

118
00:11:16,119 --> 00:11:19,008
Here, I'll take your prayer wheel.
來，我幫你拿轉經輪

119
00:11:24,078 --> 00:11:27,030
Help her to get up. 扶她起來吧
That's good. 嗯好了

120
00:11:35,077 --> 00:11:39,155
- Now sit down here. 好，坐這邊
- And look that way.現在看這裡喔

121
00:11:43,005 --> 00:11:47,035
- Yes, this way. 對，看這邊
- You have to look that way. 你要看這邊唷

122
00:11:49,142 --> 00:11:51,042
This way! 這邊！

123
00:11:55,091 --> 00:11:58,207
- You'll have to change the photo. 
你趕快換一下照片好了
- Yes, change it. 對，換一下好了

124
00:12:02,406 --> 00:12:04,092
That's better, the ocean. 這樣好多了，海洋阿

125
00:12:06,223 --> 00:12:12,034
- The other way… 另外一邊...
- You have to look the other way. 你要看另一邊唷

126
00:12:13,231 --> 00:12:15,243
Look at me, look at me. 看著我，看著我

127
00:12:17,249 --> 00:12:19,086
Yes, look at him. 對，看著他

128
00:12:21,130 --> 00:12:23,143
One, two, three.
一、二、三

129
00:12:32,037 --> 00:12:34,049
Shall I put the rolls in the truck?
要把這一卷放在卡車上嗎？

130
00:12:34,212 --> 00:12:36,162
Hang on, we'll take this one first.
等一下，我們先把這個拿走

131
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:44,056
Make sure it's well rolled first.
確定它有捲好了喔

132
00:12:49,015 --> 00:12:51,040
Put it here for now.
把它放在這邊

133
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:54,000
Pack the clothes away now.
把衣服也收一收

134
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:10,020
Hey, kid, how are you?
哈囉，孩子你還好嗎？

135
00:13:11,018 --> 00:13:13,080
- Are you passing by Lhassa? 你會經過拉薩嗎？
- Yes. 會阿

136
00:13:15,037 --> 00:13:18,205
Take this butter to Potala Palace, 經過布達拉宮時
as an offering for my mother. 把這奶油貢給我媽

137
00:13:19,013 --> 00:13:21,013
- Yes, I promise I'll do it. 好，我保證我會
- Thank you. 謝謝你

138
00:13:33,008 --> 00:13:36,216
- Have you got all the props. 你把道具都拿齊了嗎
- Yeah, got them. 嗯都好了

139
00:13:37,127 --> 00:13:42,210
Put them away tidily, 把它們放整齊了，
so they're ready when we need them. 
這樣我們需要的時候才好找。

140
00:13:42,710 --> 00:13:44,710


141
00:13:47,028 --> 00:13:49,016
There, that's good. 嗯，這樣好

142
00:13:52,119 --> 00:13:56,233
- Where do I put them all? 這些應該放哪邊？
- In a box, so they don't break. 拿個盒子才不會破

143
00:13:59,037 --> 00:14:02,047
We'd better hurry 我們動作要快一點
before they block the road. 趕在他們封路以前

144
00:14:02,148 --> 00:14:06,690
- Why are they working at night? 他們為什麼晚上工作阿？
- To be ready for the authorities. 就為了當局囉

145
00:14:07,078 --> 00:14:11,032
- Shall we stop in Kang Ba to sleep? 
要在康巴暫停睡覺嗎？
- Yes. 嗯

146
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:15,063
- We mustn't forget the kid's butter. 
那個孩子的奶油千萬別忘
- No, no. 不會的
